&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Integrate risk analysis and mitigation in the Software Development Life Cycle.
&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Use qualitative, quantitative, and hybrid risk analysis approaches based on standardized risk analysis methods.
&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Track and manage weaknesses that are discovered throughout risk assessment, change management, and continuous monitoring.
